description.en:
Safari Holstein cow

This Holstein cow is part of the Farm-collection. Holstein cows are better known as Holstein-Friesian, and are distinguished by their black and white markings and are known for their miraculous milk production.

The product is non-toxic and BPA-free. Suitable for collectors, enthusiasts, teachers and children, you can admire it on a shelf, use it in class or just play with it.

Specifications:
Collection Farm
Colour: white, black
Gender: junior
Dimensions: 13.3 x 5 x 7.5 cm (LxWxH)
Material: plastic
Age: 4-12 years
